<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>271</hymn_number>
<key>D</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ka kut lawng in ka kai lai maw, Khamhbawi Jesuh tonnak ah, Nikhat
 hmanh A-mah ca tuan lo, Zei ka pe lo, Keimah nih.

[C1]
   Ka kut lawng in ka kai lai maw? Hi bang Khamhbawi ka hmuh lai,
   Hawikom te hmanh sawm hin loin, Zeiti'n hi bangin kai lai.

[V2]
 Ka thih lai ca ka thinphang lo, Jesuh nih a ka khamh ca'h, Hawi sawm
 loin a ka hmuh lai, Ngaihchiat loin um kho lo.

[C2]
   Ka kut lawng in ka kai lai maw? Hi bang Khamhbawi ka hmuh lai,
   Hawikom te hmanh sawm hin loin, Zeiti'n hi bangin kai lai.

[V3]
 Kum fate in ka sual lengmang, cu si ca ka hnangam lo, Jesuh nawl in um
 ka duh cang, A zungzal zulh ka duh ko.

[C3]
   Ka kut lawng in ka kai lai maw? Hi bang Khamhbawi ka hmuh lai,
   Hawikom te hmanh sawm hin loin, Zeiti'n hi bangin kai lai.

[V4]
 Maw lung thiangmi, it hlah, tho tuah, Jesuh ca rian kha tuan tuah,
 Thihnak nih an phak hlanah hin, Midang kha va forh tuah hna.

[C4]
   Ka kut lawng in ka kai lai maw? Hi bang Khamhbawi ka hmuh lai,
   Hawikom te hmanh sawm hin loin, Zeiti'n hi bangin kai lai.</lyrics>
<title>KA KUT LAWNG IN KA KAI LAI MAW? CH271</title>
</song>